channel.description:
This snippet will allow you to drop items in the Rune-Evo source and not destroy them.

In InventoryOptionsHandler.Java search for:
[code]player.getDialogueManager().startDialogue("DestroyItemOption", slotId, item);
player.getPackets().sendSound(2739, 0, 1);[/code]

Replace with this:
[code]player.getInventory().deleteItem(slotId, item);
if (player.getCharges().degradeCompletly(item))
     return;
World.addGroundItem(item, new WorldTile(player), player, false, 180, true);
player.getPackets().sendSound(2739, 0, 1);[/code]



Now this snippet will make it destroy a certain object when dropped.

In InventoryOptionsHandler.Java search for:
[code]if (player.getPetManager().spawnPet(itemId, true)) {
     return;
}[/code]

Below that add this:
[code]if (itemId == 995) { //Destroys Money
     player.getDialogueManager().startDialogue("DestroyItemOption", slotId, item);
     return;
}[/code]
